Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.64,0:00:21.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So you're finally here, then, you scrubs?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.28,0:00:39.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Come, now...\Nwhat are you waiting for?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.96,0:00:49.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,How delightful!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.69,0:01:15.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Master, it's time\Nfor the regular debriefing.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.49,0:01:18.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Time does fly, doesn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.95,0:01:24.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Good job, all of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.25,0:01:27.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Come back anytime to try again!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.80,0:01:38.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Master, what were you watching while\Nsparring with the prospective students?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.30,0:01:39.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Phoenix Festa, of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.76,0:01:43.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hu Feng, I just saw the most\Ndelightful boy in the latest match!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.85,0:01:46.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Seidoukan's Ayato Amagiri\Nor something?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.60,0:01:49.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,In terms of raw talent,\NI think that kid was the best!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.73,0:01:51.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Such a blast to watch!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.98,0:01:54.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Is it too late to ask him to play for us?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.03,0:01:56.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Easier said than done.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.16,0:02:00.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,However, it seems\Nthat his powers are limited.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.58,0:02:02.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But that's what makes him\Nall the more intriguing!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.54,0:02:07.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If I'm not mistaken, his next\Nopponents are Song and Luo.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.67,0:02:09.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't be more envious!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.58,0:02:12.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So there you are, Master.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.00,0:02:14.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, and you, too, Elder Brother Zhao.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.88,0:02:16.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- It's been a long time.\N- It's been a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.43,0:02:18.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's the twins, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.93,0:02:20.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Shenyun and Shenhua...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.72,0:02:22.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So, what did you want to see me for?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.72,0:02:27.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, at this rate, we're headed for a clash\Nwith Song and Luo in the sixth round.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.73,0:02:31.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Being from the Water faction, we just\Ndon't see eye to eye with the Wood faction.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.90,0:02:33.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,When we do clash with them...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.44,0:02:35.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...we might go a bit overboard.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.82,0:02:38.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- Just so you know.\N- Just so you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.20,0:02:39.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why, you...!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.57,0:02:43.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Just do as you please.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.58,0:02:47.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,My goal is merely\Nto endow you with power.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.83,0:02:50.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I have no interest in telling you\Nwhat path to choose.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.75,0:02:51.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.71,0:02:54.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I can see why you inherited\Nthe Divine Revelations!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.30,0:02:56.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,How open-minded you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.05,0:02:57.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- We are quite impressed!\N- We are quite impressed!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.72,0:03:02.68,Sign Left,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,AYATO AMAGIRI\NJULIS-ALEXIA VON RIESSFELD\N\N\NLUO KUNZHAN\NSONG RAN\N\N\NSHENYUN LI\NSHENHUA LI
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.97,0:03:01.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That said, are you sure\Nthat all will go as you planned?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.55,0:03:05.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,By that do you mean we do not\Nmeasure up to Song and Luo?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.60,0:03:12.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no. But we're not sure if those two\Nwill win through to the next round.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.53,0:03:23.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Master, do you believe that Song\Nand Luo will lose to that Seidoukan team,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.24,0:03:25.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,even though their weakness\Nhas been exposed?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.41,0:03:30.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All I care about is having a good time.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.00,0:03:33.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's what I'm here for.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.96,0:03:36.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If Amagiri and his\Nteammate win tomorrow,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.92,0:03:39.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,he'll only increase\Nhis capabilities further.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.01,0:03:42.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And that's what I'm looking forward to.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.93,0:03:45.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,After all, that would make it...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.02,0:03:51.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...all the more enjoyable!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.36,0:05:27.91,ArcName,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Divine Revelations
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.91,0:05:27.91,Sign,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Seidoukan's new phenom\Nmight be saddled with a time limit!?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.45,0:05:27.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.41,0:05:31.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Who knew that the rumor would\Nspread like this in a single day?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.12,0:05:35.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The players themselves must have\Nreceived even more detailed data.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.29,0:05:38.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,How much do you think they know?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.67,0:05:41.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,For starters, we should assume\Nthat the match with Irene
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.30,0:05:43.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,gave them a rough idea\Nof your time limit.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.67,0:05:45.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, probably.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.18,0:05:47.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The real issue is
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.22,0:05:51.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,that the word's out about the impact\Non you when you release those powers.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.10,0:05:55.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"In order to recover\Nfrom the physical damage of this impact,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.85,0:05:59.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,it can be inferred that Amagiri must\Nstand by for a certain interval..."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.65,0:06:02.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I hear that Rewolf is the source\Nof these rumors!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.73,0:06:04.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That wretched Tyrant!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.86,0:06:08.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.24,0:06:10.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,how are you really feeling?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.66,0:06:14.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I still have some pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.50,0:06:17.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But not enough to keep me\Nfrom fighting normally.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.71,0:06:20.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So you won't be able to go all-out, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.34,0:06:23.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No... I don't think that's gonna happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.21,0:06:28.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Very well. In that case,\Nthere are two things I want to confirm.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.05,0:06:33.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,How can your defense be so formidable\Nwhen your powers are sealed?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.52,0:06:34.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.43,0:06:38.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If it's defense, I can get by with experience\Nand anticipation up to a point.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.60,0:06:39.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.61,0:06:42.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All right, here's the other thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.11,0:06:45.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That method you have of releasing\Nyour power for just a second...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.07,0:06:46.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Can you still use it, even now?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.61,0:06:51.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I think I could pull it off at least once.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.62,0:06:53.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Very well, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.91,0:06:57.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Our next opponents\Nare Jie Long's Rank #20 and 23.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.91,0:07:03.42,Sign,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,DIVINE REVELATIONS
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.42,0:07:02.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,They're direct disciples of Jie Long's\Nstudent council president,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.00,0:07:04.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"Divine Revelations,"\Nand masters of close combat.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.13,0:07:08.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If you were at full strength,\Nit wouldn't be hard to defeat them,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.63,0:07:11.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,but frankly, in your current state,\Nthat would be asking too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.39,0:07:15.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If it were one-on-one,\NI'm sure I could hold my own,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.72,0:07:17.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,but taking on both at the same time...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.06,0:07:20.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Which brings me to my proposal.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.81,0:07:22.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You have a plan?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.86,0:07:24.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think of this strategy?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.73,0:07:27.99,Sign,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,PHOENIX FESTA\NROUND 5\NMATCH #8
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.99,0:07:29.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Here we are!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.03,0:07:31.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The last match of Round 5\Nof the Phoenix Festa!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.28,0:07:35.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Which team will claim\Nthe final berth of the quarterfinals?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.66,0:07:38.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Since this year's teams\Nare of a high caliber,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.83,0:07:41.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'd say every one of them\Nhas a shot at winning it all!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.04,0:07:47.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Now, then, why don't we introduce\Nthe quarterfinalists to watch?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.55,0:07:50.18,Sign,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,First of all, this year's front-runners!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.18,0:07:54.68,Sign,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Arlequint's all-powerful,\Nbleeding-edge puppets, AR-D and RM-C!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.68,0:07:57.64,Sign,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,They'll be competing as Ernesta\Nand Camilla's surrogates!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.89,0:08:03.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What a shock to see them win after allowing\Ntheir opponents to attack for a full minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.23,0:08:05.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And here are Jie Long's\Nprized twin demons!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.98,0:08:07.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Shenyun Li,\Na.k.a. Phantom Fog Disperser,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.57,0:08:09.86,Sign Left NB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,SHENHUA LI
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.57,0:08:09.86,Sign Right NB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,SHENYUN LI
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.78,0:08:10.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and Shenhua Li,\Na.k.a. Phantom Creator!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.61,0:08:13.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,With their huge arsenal\Nof Star Senjutsu combo moves,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.62,0:08:15.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,they're devilishly hard to beat.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.87,0:08:20.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Till now, they've had their way with\Nall the opponents and gone on to win!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.58,0:08:21.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But wait, there's more!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.87,0:08:25.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Fighting for the Silver-winged Knights'\Npride and honor!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.04,0:08:29.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Elliot Forster and Doroteo Lemus\Nof Galahadworth!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.46,0:08:34.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Doroteo's a beast of a veteran.\NThis is his third Festa.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.47,0:08:35.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Elliot is a young prodigy
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.72,0:08:39.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,who joined the Silver-winged Knights\Ndespite only being in junior high!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.14,0:08:42.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Seidoukan Academy owns\Nthe Phoenix Festa!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.56,0:08:44.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Can they stand their ground?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.15,0:08:47.48,Sign Right NB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,KIRIN TOUDOU
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.15,0:08:47.48,Sign Left NB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,SAYA SASAMIYA
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.73,0:08:47.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kirin Toudou and Saya Sasamiya!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.98,0:08:50.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The teamwork between Toudou,\Nwho's adept at close combat,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.44,0:08:54.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and Sasamiya, who has sheer firepower...\Nthey're totally in the zone!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.61,0:08:57.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But speaking of Seidoukan Academy,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.62,0:09:00.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,we also need to keep an eye\Non the Amagiri-Riessfeld team,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.75,0:09:02.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,who are up next!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.16,0:09:02.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.16,0:09:06.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}They sure handed Irene,\Narmed with the Ogre Lux "Gravi-sheath,"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.96,0:09:08.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and her teammate Priscilla,\Na resounding defeat!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.92,0:09:12.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Meanwhile, all kinds of rumors\Nhave started swirling about Amagiri!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.05,0:09:17.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If what's being reported is true,\Nthe disadvantage will be huge!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.51,0:09:21.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Has he recovered from the damage\Nhe sustained in releasing his powers?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.14,0:09:24.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And will we get to see that performance\Nfrom him again today?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.98,0:09:28.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}All right! This is the match to watch,\Nin every sense of the word!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.31,0:09:32.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Seidoukan Academy's Ayato Amagiri\Nand Julis-Alexia von Riessfeld!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.61,0:09:33.61,Sign Right NB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,SONG RAN
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.61,0:09:33.61,Sign Left NB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,LUO KUNZHAN
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.28,0:09:40.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And now Jie Long 7th Academy's\NSong and Luo have arrived onstage!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.87,0:09:42.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Amagiri!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.16,0:09:46.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Whether or not those rumors\Nabout you are true,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.88,0:09:49.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Luo and I plan to go all-out against you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.17,0:09:51.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,To be honest,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.30,0:09:54.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,we would've preferred to go head-to-head\Nwith you when you were 100%.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.84,0:09:57.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But such are the rules\Nof the team-oriented Phoenix Festa!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.39,0:09:59.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't take it personally!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.39,0:10:01.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, hey, no need to...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.14,0:10:04.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We just wanted to let you\Nknow that before the match.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.68,0:10:05.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.77,0:10:07.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.19,0:10:10.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So they're true warriors,\Nthrough and through.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.94,0:10:12.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Who knew guys like that existed?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.11,0:10:19.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}All right, both teams are now onstage!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.45,0:10:24.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,They're going start off by testing you\Nto see whether you can fight at 100%.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.41,0:10:27.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And they'll see through it right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.25,0:10:29.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That it's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.46,0:10:30.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Probably...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.42,0:10:33.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All right! Listen up, Ayato.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.42,0:10:36.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This is your mark.\NMake sure you remember it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.88,0:10:37.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.30,0:10:40.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The signal's the fireworks, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.68,0:10:42.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Make sure you've met\Nall the conditions by then.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.39,0:10:44.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Roger that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.10,0:10:51.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Now which team is going to seize victory{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.02,0:10:54.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}in this fifth round match\Nand head to the quarterfinals?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.53,0:10:58.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Match #8, Round 5 of the Phoenix Festa!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.86,0:11:00.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Battle...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.24,0:11:02.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...start!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.33,0:11:10.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Here we come!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.43,0:11:23.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.06,0:11:27.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like the rumors were true.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.69,0:11:31.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Burst into bloom, Primrose!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.70,0:11:43.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, Ayato! He got past me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.38,0:12:01.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Can you endure this blow?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.34,0:12:03.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Whoa!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.60,0:12:07.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Amagiri is under siege!\NWhat an unexpected turn of events!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.68,0:12:11.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The Song-Luo team's concerted\Nattack was surely masterful!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.48,0:12:13.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No sign of that performance this time,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.31,0:12:15.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and he's using far less Prana\Nthan what we've seen till now.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.57,0:12:19.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So I guess those rumors\Nmust be true, right?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.91,0:12:26.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Come out, Loropetalum!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.63,0:12:41.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Could this be one of Riessfeld's skills?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.55,0:12:44.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A wall of flames has appeared\Nout of nowhere!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.01,0:12:45.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's split the stage in two!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.51,0:12:50.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I see, so you've separated Luo and me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.64,0:12:53.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Now it's one-on-one.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.65,0:12:56.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You believe you have a chance\Nif it's one-on-one?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.56,0:12:58.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,To be honest,\NI don't think it'll be easy,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.90,0:13:02.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,but that doesn't mean\NI should give up, does it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.36,0:13:06.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That was a stupid question to ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.87,0:13:08.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Allow me to apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.08,0:13:14.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.04,0:13:16.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I see that you've been\Nover-hyped, Glühen Rose!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.67,0:13:18.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This is the skill of a Rank #23?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.05,0:13:21.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}At Seidoukan, you'd easily\Ncrack the Page One ranks!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.51,0:13:25.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Livingstone Daisy!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.85,0:13:33.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I see... So that's what's going on.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.10,0:13:36.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're expending your power\Nto maintain this wall of flames, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.15,0:13:39.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But you could've turned this\Ninto a one-on-one battle
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.69,0:13:43.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,without resorting\Nto such elaborate tricks.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.15,0:13:44.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I had no choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.61,0:13:47.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This is the only way we can win.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.16,0:13:52.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Meaning that you have\Nsomething else up your sleeve, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.00,0:14:01.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,To be honest, I admire you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.13,0:14:03.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You may have been focusing on defense,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.92,0:14:06.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,but to withstand\Nall of my attacks till now...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.34,0:14:11.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If you were at full strength,\Nour roles might have been reversed.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.27,0:14:16.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No, I don't think\NI could've held out for so long.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.40,0:14:18.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.07,0:14:21.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,that's necessarily true.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.32,0:14:26.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But I couldn't live with myself\Nif I went on battering you like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.86,0:14:28.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Out of respect for you,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.07,0:14:31.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I shall finish this with my next move.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.91,0:14:35.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All right, you'd better hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.46,0:14:39.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Or else the battle\Nbeyond that wall will be over.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.46,0:14:42.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Are you perhaps implying\Nthat my partner will lose?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.55,0:14:45.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,In his current state,\NMurakumo has no chance against us.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.80,0:14:46.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Am I right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.72,0:14:47.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Absolutely.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.18,0:14:50.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,For Ayato to defeat you\Nin his current state,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.80,0:14:53.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,the best he could do would be\Nto catch you off-guard somehow.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.47,0:14:58.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, not that Song and I would\Never lay ourselves open like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.40,0:15:00.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That side, eh?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.04,0:15:18.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you protect yourself,\Nthis fist will pulverize everything!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.46,0:15:23.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I would advise you to dodge it,\Nrather than block it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.00,0:15:24.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Julis...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.17,0:15:26.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This is it!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.18,0:15:30.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Burst into bloom...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.93,0:15:32.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No way am I gonna let you do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.85,0:15:34.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Amaryllis! Twin Blossoms!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.19,0:15:41.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Julis's signal!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.59,0:16:07.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Badge broken!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.13,0:16:14.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,E-End of match!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.01,0:16:21.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Winners, Ayato Amagiri\Nand Julis-Alexia von Riessfeld!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.73,0:16:24.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It was stunning teamwork\Ncatching their opponents off-guard{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.19,0:16:26.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and snatching victory\Nfrom the jaws of defeat!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.65,0:16:30.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No, no, it wasn't quite\Nthat simple, actually.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.28,0:16:31.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Meaning?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.53,0:16:34.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Song was in close-quarter combat\Nwith Amagiri,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.87,0:16:38.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}whereas Luo was countering\NRiessfeld's long-distance assault.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.37,0:16:43.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}By switching places, the Seidoukan team\Nmessed up their opponents' timing,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.63,0:16:45.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and that's how they caught them\Noff-guard so decisively.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.96,0:16:48.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Really, that was amazing!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.09,0:16:54.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, we did scratch out a win, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.09,0:16:57.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Even so, it's significant\Nthat we managed to get through today.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.31,0:16:58.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,After a full day's rest tomorrow,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.93,0:17:02.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,you should be able to go all-out\Nin our next match, won't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.77,0:17:05.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, that won't be a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.48,0:17:07.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But what about you, Julis?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.65,0:17:09.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What about your injuries?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.03,0:17:12.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it doesn't seem to be broken,\Nso it's nothing I can't handle.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.95,0:17:14.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, about our next match...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.12,0:17:19.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you're able to go all-out,\Nour opponents look to be quite a handful.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.08,0:17:19.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.58,0:17:21.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I agree.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.00,0:17:28.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure you're not here\Nto offer your congratulations,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.55,0:17:31.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,so what is it that you want with us?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.55,0:17:32.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, that's precisely it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.30,0:17:37.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It was you who came up with that\Nstrategy, wasn't it, Glühen Rose?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.97,0:17:39.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.14,0:17:41.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It was an amazing combination\Nthat couldn't be achieved
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.31,0:17:43.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,unless you trusted each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.56,0:17:47.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We got trounced today.\NYou were amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.65,0:17:52.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,W-Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.11,0:17:53.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But you must be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.78,0:17:57.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Such a strategy will have no impact\Non your next opponents.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.53,0:17:58.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean by that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.12,0:18:00.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This is purely a warning.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.99,0:18:02.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Just take it at face value.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.12,0:18:06.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's easy for you to say, but our\Nnext opponents are comrades of yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.92,0:18:08.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Do you really think\NI can trust what you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.88,0:18:12.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Going to the same school\Ndoesn't make us all comrades.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.21,0:18:16.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Shenyun Li and Shenhua Li... and us...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.72,0:18:21.89,Sign Left Mid,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,LUO KUNZHAN\NSONG RAN
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.72,0:18:21.89,Sign Left,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,AYATO AMAGIRI\NJULIS-ALEXIA VON RIESSFELD
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.55,0:18:18.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We just don't see eye to eye.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.51,0:18:21.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That said, we're not about to clue you in\Non their weak points, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.47,0:18:26.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We feel more of an affinity\Nfor you two than for those twins.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.90,0:18:29.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And so we wanted\Nto show you our support.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.98,0:18:32.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All right, then, let me ask you again.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.90,0:18:35.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you say\Nour strategy wouldn't work?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.86,0:18:39.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Because when it comes to deception,\Ntrickery and surprise attacks,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.12,0:18:42.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,those twins' talents are prodigious.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.87,0:18:45.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,They'll see right through\Nany strategy you come up with,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.21,0:18:47.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and they'll be sure to one-up you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.08,0:18:49.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,In battle, you two see\Nyour opponents as your equals,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.79,0:18:52.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,embracing the risks\Nsuch a strategy entails.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.30,0:18:55.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But those two are different.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.63,0:18:57.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,They constantly look down\Non their opponents,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.43,0:18:59.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,never exposing themselves\Nto danger, no matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.51,0:19:02.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's the Li twins' way.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.39,0:19:06.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And that's what we can't\Nstomach about them.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.18,0:19:07.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, well, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.65,0:19:11.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,First you go down in inglorious defeat...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.31,0:19:15.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And now you're poisoning\Nyour opponents with trash talk?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.24,0:19:17.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.36,0:19:21.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nice to meet you,\NGlühen Rose and Murakumo.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.83,0:19:24.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Shenyun Li.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.79,0:19:26.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Shenhua Li.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.29,0:19:30.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- Pleased to make your acquaintance!\N- Pleased to make your acquaintance!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.00,0:19:32.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.38,0:19:35.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, we just felt\Nthat we owed you an apology.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.42,0:19:36.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Apology?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.42,0:19:41.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, as it seems that our comrades there\Nput up such a lame fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.76,0:19:45.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,As students of the same master,\Nwe couldn't be more mortified!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.60,0:19:49.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I don't think it was lame at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.19,0:19:55.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's worrysome for disciples of the Divine\NRevelations to be seen as so hapless.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.23,0:19:59.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So we're going to show you a world\Nour older comrades weren't able to.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.66,0:20:04.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- The depths of Star Senjutsu, that is!\N- The depths of Star Senjutsu, that is!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.04,0:20:08.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Pretty unpleasant duo, weren't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.16,0:20:14.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But including those two, three more\Nvictories, and we stand to win it all.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.75,0:20:16.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Three times, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.50,0:20:18.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Doesn't seem like a lot,\Nbut it sounds so demanding.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.55,0:20:21.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad you recognize that, at least.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.84,0:20:26.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But have you given any thought\Nto what you're going to ask for if we win?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.06,0:20:30.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I can't really think\Nof anything right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.19,0:20:32.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I had a feeling you'd say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.65,0:20:38.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm grateful to you for fighting\Nfor me, and to be honest...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.40,0:20:41.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Um, it makes me happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.28,0:20:46.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But I think it's about time you set\Nyour sights on what you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.58,0:20:49.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That may be true, but still...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.50,0:20:55.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Your older sister... what about her?
