Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.89,0:21:11.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah... Well, that's true, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.89,0:21:13.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me that you...
