Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.83,0:21:29.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Uh, before you do,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.62,0:21:31.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}you should know\Nthat you have another guest...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.96,0:21:34.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Is it all right if we let her in?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.21,0:21:35.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A guest?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.33,0:21:37.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's right. To see Riessfeld.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.34,0:21:39.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,To see me?
